title: New: Future Jr. – Tell Me That I'm Wrong
body:
Some slick electro-pop from Brisbane’s Matthew Nainby aka **Future Jr.**

– sort of what I imagine Toro y Moi covering Bieber’s recent album might sound like. Check out Tell Me That I’m Wrong below.

Like this? Follow our [On Repeat Playlist](https://open.spotify.com/user/crackintheroad/playlist/1UB6gJIZpmiO0H2zmSbg02) for a handpicked selection of the very best in new music; updated weekly.
